data.description: Charming 3 bedroom ranch in Muskegon township on a beautiful corner lot. The main level has a spacious living room with fireplace, updated kitchen, and hardwood floors throughout. Other amenities include a full basement with a finished bedroom and recreation area, fenced in backyard, and an oversized one stall garage with workshop attached. This home is neat and clean and ready for a new owner! Schedule your showing today.
